    <detaileddescription>
<para>allows several threads to work on a group of tasks in isolation (in one arena): they cannot steal outside tasks until the all these tasks are finished; this solves the issue of recursive calling of the function where <ref refid="structMR_1_1TbbTaskArenaAndGroup" kindref="compound">TbbTaskArenaAndGroup</ref> was created </para>
